Sun Dec 10 2006 Kirill Müller <mail@kirill-mueller.de>
	* cvsgui_protocol
	- Fix typo that caused errors in the analysis of the cvsgui stream
	* WinCvs
	- Better handling of bad cvsgui protocol data
	- Report to console if the cvs process has been killed (in contrast to exiting voluntarily with a proper exit code)
	- Refactor diff of two files in GraphView -- remove the second file from MultiFilesEntry instead of skipping it
	- Refactor launchCVS() for temp files -- new function createCVSTempFile()
	* Common
	- New feature "Fetch all files at once" for external diff. One cvs update command is issued for each diffed file, leading to at most two invocations of cvs (instead of n or 2n invocations for n files). New checkbox in diff dialog (WinCvs only), the setting is called "P_DiffBulkUpdate" (all platforms).
	- Proper indentation

