	* WinCvs 2.0.3 / Macros:
	- Converted first round of macros from PromptEditMessage to CvsPrompt
	  (ChangeRepo, ChangeRoot, cvs2cl, EditFileTypeAssoc, ExtendedAddTk, SearchLogComments and TagAndUpdate)

