Wed Feb 5 2003 Karl-Heinz Bruenen <gcvs@bruenen-net.de>
	* gcvs 1.1:
	- #679386: 'commitid/kopt in (r)log' patch added 
	  (thanks to Hartmut Honisch <hhonisch@users.sourceforge.net>)
