Wed Sep 27 2000 Alexandre Parenteau  <aubonbeurre@hotmail.com>
	* MacCvs 3.1.8 : Refresh bug when trashing.
	* MacCvs 3.1.8 : Tried to fix rsh : no luck. Deep GUSI problem.
